<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<mvt:item name="html_profile" />
<head>
	<mvt:if expr="g.useDevResources EQ 1"><mvt:item name="head" param="css_list_dev" /><mvt:else><mvt:item name="head" param="css_list" /></mvt:if>
	<mvt:item name="head" param="head_tag" />
	<mvt:comment>
		Sinister Diesel Homepage V2. Inactive template. Do not activate over SFNT.
		Required V2 global layer files:
		- cssui-global-header-v2.mvt
		- cssui-mega-menu-v2.mvt
		- cssui-search-console-v2.mvt
		- sd2-v2-garage-selector.mvt
		- sd2-v2-cart-drawer.mvt
		- cssui-global-footer-v2.mvt
		Canonical partial references:
		- sd2-v2-perfstrip.mvt
		- sd2-v2-product-card.mvt
		- sd2-v2-build-story.mvt
	</mvt:comment>
</head>
<body>
	<mvt:item name="hdft" param="global_header" />
	<mvt:item name="hdft" param="header" />

<div class="sd2-v2-home" data-v2-home>
	<section class="sd2-v2-home-hero" aria-labelledby="sd2-v2-home-hero-title">
		<div class="sd2-wrap">
			<div class="sd2-v2-home-hero__frame">
				<div class="sd2-v2-home-hero__copy">
					<p class="sd2-eyebrow">Diesel Performance, Built With Intent</p>
					<h1 class="sd2-v2-home-hero__title" id="sd2-v2-home-hero-title">Parts for trucks that work harder than the catalog says they should.</h1>
					<p class="sd2-body">Shop Powerstroke, Duramax, and Cummins parts through a V2 experience built around fitment, proof, and real garage context.</p>
					<div class="sd2-v2-home-hero__actions">
						<button class="sd2-btn sd2-btn--primary" type="button" data-v2-garage-toggle>Build Around My Truck</button>
						<a class="sd2-btn sd2-btn--outline" href="&mvte:urls:CTGYENGV2:auto;">Shop Platforms</a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="sd2-v2-home-hero__media" aria-label="Sinister Diesel shop truck placeholder">
					<img src="https://sinisterdiesel.com/mm5/graphics/00000001/8/Generated%20image%201.png" alt="Placeholder Sinister Diesel truck image">
				</div>
				<div class="sd2-v2-home-hero__factline">
					<span>MADE AND TESTED IN THE USA</span>
					<span>SINCE 2008</span>
					<span>FITMENT-FIRST V2 EXPERIENCE</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="sd2-v2-perfstrip" aria-label="Sinister Diesel proof points">
		<div class="sd2-wrap">
			<div class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__grid">
				<div class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__item"><span class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__value" data-v2-count-to="2008">2008</span><span class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__label">SINCE</span></div>
				<div class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__item"><span class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__value">USA</span><span class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__label">DESIGNED AND TESTED</span></div>
				<div class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__item"><span class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__value">FORD</span><span class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__label">POWERSTROKE</span></div>
				<div class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__item"><span class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__value">GM</span><span class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__label">DURAMAX</span></div>
				<div class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__item"><span class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__value">RAM</span><span class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__label">CUMMINS</span></div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="sd2-section sd2-v2-home-platforms" aria-labelledby="sd2-v2-platforms-title">
		<div class="sd2-wrap">
			<div class="sd2-v2-section-head">
				<p class="sd2-eyebrow">Shop By Platform</p>
				<h2 class="sd2-heading-lg" id="sd2-v2-platforms-title">Start with the truck, then narrow the build.</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="sd2-v2-platform-grid">
				<a class="sd2-v2-platform-card sd2-v2-platform-card--large" href="&mvte:urls:CTGYENGV2:auto;">
					<img src="https://sinisterdiesel.com/mm5/graphics/00000001/8/Generated%20image%201.png" alt="Ford Powerstroke placeholder">
					<span>Powerstroke</span>
				</a>
				<a class="sd2-v2-platform-card" href="&mvte:urls:CTGYENGV2:auto;">
					<img src="https://sinisterdiesel.com/mm5/graphics/00000001/8/Generated%20image%203.png" alt="GM Duramax placeholder">
					<span>Duramax</span>
				</a>
				<a class="sd2-v2-platform-card" href="&mvte:urls:CTGYENGV2:auto;">
					<img src="https://sinisterdiesel.com/mm5/graphics/00000001/8/Generated%20image%202.png" alt="Ram Cummins placeholder">
					<span>Cummins</span>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="sd2-section--tight sd2-v2-home-garage" aria-labelledby="sd2-v2-garage-title">
		<div class="sd2-wrap">
			<div class="sd2-v2-garage-prompt">
				<div>
					<p class="sd2-eyebrow">My Garage</p>
					<h2 class="sd2-heading-lg" id="sd2-v2-garage-title">Save your truck before you shop.</h2>
					<p class="sd2-body">The V2 garage keeps the active vehicle available to future fitment, category, product, and account experiences.</p>
				</div>
				<button class="sd2-btn sd2-btn--primary" type="button" data-v2-garage-toggle>Add Your Truck</button>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="sd2-section sd2-v2-home-products" aria-labelledby="sd2-v2-products-title">
		<div class="sd2-wrap">
			<div class="sd2-v2-section-head">
				<p class="sd2-eyebrow">Featured Parts</p>
				<h2 class="sd2-heading-lg" id="sd2-v2-products-title">Placeholder products pending real Miva product binding.</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="sd2-v2-product-grid">
				<article class="sd2-card sd2-v2-product-card sd2-v2-product-card--hero">
					<a class="sd2-v2-product-card__media" href="&mvte:urls:CTGYLISTV2:auto;">
						<img src="https://sinisterdiesel.com/mm5/graphics/00000001/8/Generated%20image%201.png" alt="Placeholder featured Powerstroke part">
						<span class="sd2-v2-product-card__flag">PLACEHOLDER</span>
					</a>
					<div class="sd2-v2-product-card__body">
						<p class="sd2-v2-product-card__platform">Powerstroke</p>
						<h3 class="sd2-v2-product-card__title"><a href="&mvte:urls:CTGYLISTV2:auto;">Intercooler and pipe systems</a></h3>
						<p class="sd2-v2-product-card__note">Representative category card until real product data is wired.</p>
						<div class="sd2-v2-product-card__foot"><span class="sd2-v2-product-card__price">Miva price pending</span><a class="sd2-v2-product-card__link" href="&mvte:urls:CTGYLISTV2:auto;">View</a></div>
					</div>
				</article>
				<article class="sd2-card sd2-v2-product-card">
					<a class="sd2-v2-product-card__media" href="&mvte:urls:CTGYLISTV2:auto;"><img src="https://sinisterdiesel.com/mm5/graphics/00000001/8/Generated%20image%202.png" alt="Placeholder filtration product"><span class="sd2-v2-product-card__flag">PLACEHOLDER</span></a>
					<div class="sd2-v2-product-card__body"><p class="sd2-v2-product-card__platform">Filtration</p><h3 class="sd2-v2-product-card__title"><a href="&mvte:urls:CTGYLISTV2:auto;">Coolant and oil filtration</a></h3><p class="sd2-v2-product-card__note">Real product binding pending.</p><div class="sd2-v2-product-card__foot"><span class="sd2-v2-product-card__price">Miva price pending</span><a class="sd2-v2-product-card__link" href="&mvte:urls:CTGYLISTV2:auto;">View</a></div></div>
				</article>
				<article class="sd2-card sd2-v2-product-card">
					<a class="sd2-v2-product-card__media" href="&mvte:urls:CTGYLISTV2:auto;"><img src="https://sinisterdiesel.com/mm5/graphics/00000001/8/Generated%20image%203.png" alt="Placeholder turbo product"><span class="sd2-v2-product-card__flag">PLACEHOLDER</span></a>
					<div class="sd2-v2-product-card__body"><p class="sd2-v2-product-card__platform">Airflow</p><h3 class="sd2-v2-product-card__title"><a href="&mvte:urls:CTGYLISTV2:auto;">Turbo systems</a></h3><p class="sd2-v2-product-card__note">Real product binding pending.</p><div class="sd2-v2-product-card__foot"><span class="sd2-v2-product-card__price">Miva price pending</span><a class="sd2-v2-product-card__link" href="&mvte:urls:CTGYLISTV2:auto;">View</a></div></div>
				</article>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="sd2-section sd2-v2-home-build" aria-labelledby="sd2-v2-build-title">
		<div class="sd2-wrap">
			<article class="sd2-v2-build-story">
				<div class="sd2-v2-build-story__media"><img src="https://sinisterdiesel.com/mm5/graphics/00000001/8/Generated%20image%203.png" alt="Placeholder diesel build story"></div>
				<div class="sd2-v2-build-story__body">
					<p class="sd2-eyebrow">Build Story</p>
					<h2 class="sd2-heading-lg" id="sd2-v2-build-title">Tow rig setup, built around reliability.</h2>
					<p class="sd2-body">Placeholder editorial content pending a real build story. The approved structure supports real truck context, parts used, install notes, and proof links.</p>
					<blockquote class="sd2-v2-build-story__quote">"The goal is confidence under load, not noise for its own sake."</blockquote>
				</div>
				<aside class="sd2-v2-build-story__specs" aria-label="Build specifications">
					<div><span>Platform</span><strong>Duramax</strong></div>
					<div><span>Use Case</span><strong>Towing</strong></div>
					<div><span>Data</span><strong>Pending</strong></div>
				</aside>
			</article>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="sd2-section--tight sd2-v2-home-trust" aria-labelledby="sd2-v2-trust-title">
		<div class="sd2-wrap">
			<div class="sd2-v2-section-head"><p class="sd2-eyebrow">Proof Points</p><h2 class="sd2-heading-lg" id="sd2-v2-trust-title">Specific reasons to trust the build.</h2></div>
			<div class="sd2-v2-trust-grid">
				<div><strong>Established 2008</strong><span>Brand history stated in the existing global V2 trust bar.</span></div>
				<div><strong>USA focus</strong><span>Made and tested in the USA messaging carried from approved global layer.</span></div>
				<div><strong>Miva-safe commerce</strong><span>Basket, checkout, search, account, and URLs remain in Miva.</span></div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="sd2-section sd2-v2-home-content" aria-labelledby="sd2-v2-content-title">
		<div class="sd2-wrap">
			<div class="sd2-v2-content-teaser">
				<div><p class="sd2-eyebrow">Learn Before You Buy</p><h2 class="sd2-heading-lg" id="sd2-v2-content-title">Guides, installs, and build notes belong beside the parts.</h2></div>
				<a class="sd2-btn sd2-btn--outline" href="&mvte:urls:NEWS:auto;">View Guides</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</div>

	<mvt:item name="hdft" param="footer" />
	<mvt:item name="hdft" param="global_footer" />
</body>
</html>
